This project contains source code cloned from the original Monit project
(https://bitbucket.org/tildeslash/monit), with modifications made by the
Project Clearwater (http://www.projectclearwater.org/) team.

All source code, including modifications, is freely available and hosted
in the clearwater-monit github repository
(https://github.com/Metaswitch/clearwater-monit).

All modifications made to the original project can be seen in the commit history
of the clearwater-monit project in the github repository linked above.

This project is provided under the original Monit license terms, as found in
the COPYING file (https://github.com/Metaswitch/clearwater-monit/blob/master/COPYING).
